org.opensha2.data

  • Packages that use org.opensha2.data 
    Package Description
    org.opensha2.calc
    Hazard calculation classes and utilties.
    org.opensha2.data
    Classes and utilities for working with array and List based data and xy data sequences.
    org.opensha2.eq.model
    Provides the Source representations and containers, as well as GroundMotionModel containers for use in a HazardModel.
    org.opensha2.mfd
    Classes and utilties for working with magnitude frequency distributions (MFDs).
    org.opensha2.programs
    Entry points for conducting probabilisitic seismic hazard analysis (PSHA) calculations.
